Bring out Mr. Du!

4
00:01:33,880 --> 00:01:35,080
Pay back the money you owe the bank. Hurry up!

5
00:01:35,110 --> 00:01:36,520
-Yes, pay the money back! 
 -That’s right, pay it back!

6
00:01:36,550 --> 00:01:37,630
-Pay it back! 
 -Exactly, hurry and pay!

7
00:01:37,670 --> 00:01:39,170
Everyone, calm down!

8
00:01:39,310 --> 00:01:41,390
Our young master is grieving right now.

9
00:01:41,670 --> 00:01:43,200
Please allow us a few days of leniency.

10
00:01:43,229 --> 00:01:44,150
Get out of the way!

11
00:01:44,470 --> 00:01:45,880
Bring out your Mr. Du to pay us back.

12
00:01:45,910 --> 00:01:46,750
Hurry up!

13
00:01:47,470 --> 00:01:48,950
Now that Military Governor Du is gone,

14
00:01:49,070 --> 00:01:50,180
