15
00:01:50,350 --> 00:01:52,060
this debt will turn into a bad loan!

16
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:52,870
That’s right!

17
00:01:52,910 --> 00:01:53,520
Ladies and gentlemen,

18
00:01:53,550 --> 00:01:55,030
