24
00:02:04,310 --> 00:02:05,270
And who are you?

25
00:02:05,310 --> 00:02:06,150
Exactly.

26
00:02:07,150 --> 00:02:08,350
You’re just a young woman.

27
00:02:08,910 --> 00:02:10,289
What can you do?

28
00:02:10,430 --> 00:02:12,430
