35
00:02:22,030 --> 00:02:23,030
Go help her.

36
00:02:23,710 --> 00:02:24,630
Me?

37
00:02:25,590 --> 00:02:27,270
Alright, I’ll help.

38
00:02:31,430 --> 00:02:32,470
Now, each of you

39
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:33,590
