40
00:02:33,710 --> 00:02:34,920
which bank you’re from,

41
00:02:35,070 --> 00:02:35,910
when the debt was incurred,

42
00:02:36,030 --> 00:02:38,079
how much was borrowed, and the interest rate.

43
00:02:38,190 --> 00:02:39,360
I will write it all down clearly

44
00:02:39,550 --> 00:02:40,510
