Fine.

50
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:51,390
I represent Jincheng Bank.

51
00:02:51,550 --> 00:02:52,310
Three years ago,

52
00:02:52,340 --> 00:02:53,820
Military Governor Du took out a loan with us.

53
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,600
