54
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,030
Mine.

55
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,350
Mine.

56
00:03:05,750 --> 00:03:06,590
And mine.

57
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:07,580
Mine.

58
00:03:07,830 --> 00:03:08,630
Mine.

59
00:03:11,070 --> 00:03:12,550
Young Marshal Chi, what's on your mind?

60
00:03:13,230 --> 00:03:15,270
Is this even the Zhou Yumian I know?

61
00:03:15,740 --> 00:03:17,900
This young woman is actually stepping up to handle things.

62
00:03:20,750 --> 00:03:21,820
Are you sure

63
00:03:21,990 --> 00:03:23,340
you ever truly knew

64
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:25,310
