79
00:04:15,780 --> 00:04:16,660
Let’s go.

80
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,610
-Let’s go.
-Let’s go.

81
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:25,500
Wenlan,

82
00:04:26,350 --> 00:04:27,750
