92
00:05:01,630 --> 00:05:02,950
and repay the bank debts.

93
00:05:03,350 --> 00:05:04,470
And what about yourself?

94
00:05:05,470 --> 00:05:06,710
I plan to study medicine.

95
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:09,070
You once said,

96
00:05:10,190 --> 00:05:11,670
even if hope is faint,

97
00:05:11,860 --> 00:05:13,380
it is still precious.

98
00:05:14,270 --> 00:05:15,590
I want to be part

99
00:05:15,590 --> 00:05:16,550
of that hope.

100
00:05:17,330 --> 00:05:18,130
Alright.

101
00:05:18,540 --> 00:05:19,960
No matter what you do,

102
00:05:20,030 --> 00:05:21,150
I will support you

103
00:05:22,110 --> 00:05:23,830
