117
00:06:02,870 --> 00:06:03,710
Alright.

118
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,560
Wenlan,

119
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:07,590
My condolences.

120
00:06:15,090 --> 00:06:17,020
