124
00:06:26,690 --> 00:06:27,700
You want to ask me out?

125
00:06:30,130 --> 00:06:31,540
There’s a temple fair tonight.

126
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:32,670
I wonder if you

127
00:06:32,950 --> 00:06:34,540
