132
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,230
I might consider it.

133
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:56,110
Then you must consider carefully.

134
00:06:56,409 --> 00:06:57,900
I’m heading to the orphanage first.

135
00:06:58,070 --> 00:06:59,110
I promised Hai

136
00:06:59,140 --> 00:07:00,620
to take them to the temple fair.

137
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:03,370
If you make up your mind,

138
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,510
meet me at the usual spot.

139
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,920
Here's your little bunny.

140
00:07:29,030 --> 00:07:30,280
One little bunny.

141
00:07:30,310 --> 00:07:31,440
It’s mine!

142
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:33,070
Come, take it and try it.

143
00:07:34,290 --> 00:07:36,110
Is it sweet?

144
00:07:37,210 --> 00:07:37,970
Sweet!

145
00:07:57,250 --> 00:08:00,430
[Sugar figurines]

146
00:08:29,930 --> 00:08:30,890
You’re here.

147
00:08:32,630 --> 00:08:34,130
Have you been waiting long?

148
00:08:34,510 --> 00:08:35,640
I almost thought

149
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:37,240
you were going to leave me waiting here.

150
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:39,120
Sister Jiang Yao,

151
00:08:39,289 --> 00:08:40,630
isn’t he a traitor?

152
00:08:40,650 --> 00:08:43,110
Why are we walking around the temple fair with him?

153
00:08:43,350 --> 00:08:44,970
I don’t want to play with a traitor.

154
00:08:44,990 --> 00:08:46,310
I only want to play with you!

155
00:08:47,140 --> 00:08:48,060
Hai,

156
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,360
I made a mistake.

157
00:08:49,390 --> 00:08:51,160
He’s never been a traitor.

158
00:08:51,880 --> 00:08:53,160
He’s a good person.

159
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,700
Are you really the kind of good person

160
00:08:54,700 --> 00:08:56,270
who can drive bad guys away?

161
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:03,670
Yes.

162
00:09:04,350 --> 00:09:05,310
Alright then.

163
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,560
In that case, I’ll be willing to play with this uncle.

164
00:09:07,690 --> 00:09:09,480
Let’s go explore over there.

165
00:09:10,590 --> 00:09:11,290
-Let’s go. 
 -Yanzhou...

166
00:09:11,310 --> 00:09:12,310
Come here quickly.

167
00:09:14,310 --> 00:09:15,570
Sister Jiang Yao,

168
00:09:16,330 --> 00:09:18,150
is he your boyfriend?

169
00:09:19,590 --> 00:09:21,220
He’s definitely not my boyfriend,

170
00:09:21,250 --> 00:09:22,320
because he once said,

171
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,680
someone like me

172
00:09:23,700 --> 00:09:25,340
doesn’t deserve a boyfriend.

173
00:09:26,350 --> 00:09:28,350
So Miss Jiang really holds grudges, huh?

174
00:09:28,910 --> 00:09:30,750
How about I take back what I said?

175
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:42,680
Sister Jiang Yao, let’s go play over there.

176
00:10:02,730 --> 00:10:04,380
This is yours.

177
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:05,990
-I was holding it for you just now. 
 -Thank you.

178
00:10:06,030 --> 00:10:06,790
This is yours.

179
00:10:06,790 --> 00:10:07,830
The second one is mine.

180
00:10:16,130 --> 00:10:17,210
Here, take it.

181
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:19,400
Go buy something fun for everyone.

182
00:10:27,380 --> 00:10:28,220
Alright.

183
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:31,010
Let’s go buy toys!

184
00:10:31,290 --> 00:10:31,930
Alright!

185
00:10:31,950 --> 00:10:32,880
Let's go!

186
00:10:33,590 --> 00:10:34,670
Come on. Come on.

187
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,400
