193
00:10:58,110 --> 00:10:59,020
Someone this handsome?

194
00:10:59,040 --> 00:11:00,610
I’ve got to put in my best effort.

195
00:11:00,170 --> 00:11:04,700
♫Was our meeting a test of fate?♫

196
