199
00:11:15,090 --> 00:11:19,880
♫Farewells are often scenes of sorrow♫

200
00:11:20,490 --> 00:11:25,480
♫Yet I'm grateful we once shared a past♫

201
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:29,350
♫Even if it was just for a fleeting moment♫

202
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:28,680
Here, this is for you.

203
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,880
