217
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:04,510
♫Everything about you, I would choose without hesitation♫

218
00:12:04,940 --> 00:12:10,140
♫Right or wrong, as long as it's passionate at this moment♫

219
00:12:05,880 --> 00:12:07,140
Miss Jiang,

220
00:12:07,380 --> 00:12:09,020
