230
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:30,980
But I kept thinking that I couldn’t die yet.

231
00:12:31,310 --> 00:12:32,710
I had to stay alive and return to Ao City.

232
00:12:31,450 --> 00:12:36,090
♫Farewells are often scenes of sorrow♫

233
